item.description:
Trabacca is a day in a closed environment to sharpen your riding skills after a long winter. It is a NO-PRESSURE day! Do as little or much as you like or just come out an hang with us for the day.
The day will start at 9am and end whenever. We will take up a collection for pizza for lunch and bring liquids to drink during the day. There are bathroom facilities on site.
See you then!!

Where: Comcast Center
Mansfield
item.name: CANCELED Trabecca Class
